winds around 5 mph. Chance of rain 20 percent.
.TONIGHT...Partly cloudy in the evening, then clearing. Lows in
the mid 60s. East winds around 5 mph, becoming southeast after
midnight.
.FRIDAY...Mostly sunny. A chance of showers and thunderstorms in
the afternoon. Highs in the lower 90s. Southwest winds 5 to
10 mph. Chance of rain 40 percent.
.FRIDAY NIGHT...A chance of thunderstorms. Showers. Lows in the
mid 50s. North winds 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80 percent.
.SATURDAY...Mostly cloudy with a chance of showers in the
morning, then mostly sunny in the afternoon. Cooler with highs in
