30 percent.
.SATURDAY NIGHT THROUGH MONDAY NIGHT...Mostly clear. Lows in the
upper 40s. Highs in the upper 70s.
.TUESDAY THROUGH WEDNESDAY...Mostly clear. Highs in the mid 80s.
